hey! sorry no new comic again today :( just as motivation hits me hard the universe goes "ye haha nope". Hopefully it recovers fully this weekend. anyways thanks for being here! i love ya guys ❤️ 

thank you readers and most especially patrons! we do weekly game nights on our private discord server! I'm pretty active and hangout a lot there. We play among us and other games together every friday.You gain access from as little as $2 and other rewards woah! I appreciate every little support!

#animation

OH BOY AN ANNOUNCEMENT! What could it possibly be? ;D

I've never posted on IGTV before and I don't know what I'm doing. But here is my not-so-animation animation video anyway! Thank you for listening! If you do enjoy my comics, supporting me on Patreon will help me keep creating content for you and progress into making bigger and more fun stuffs! poke the link in my bio! love ya!

www.patreon.com/ohmygoles

[Repost of old comic]
I'm livestreaming tonight at 8PM BST on www.twitch.tv/ohmytinytin! please do pop by and let me doodle you! :3

We had 2 dogs when I was younger, one of them is named Lucky, he is a Japanese spitz. He hated loud sounds and was very afraid of thunder. He would crawl under the desk shaking and I remember hugging him to comfort and protect him of course and totally not because I was scared too.

Were you or are you afraid of thunder or loud sounds?

#comic #comics #childhoodmemories #childhoodmemory #cutecomics #heartwarming #nostalgia #nostalgic

Are you or anyone you know lactose intolerant?
Poli knows very well the consequences of eating anything dairy. But he never seems to learn and keeps on eating them! I can't blame him though, dairy foods are the best! Especially cheese mmmm!

We reached 2k on twitch last week yay! and we'll be celebrating it by having a smol stream party this upcoming WED 8PM BST where we play games and have art giveaways! Anyone is welcome to join! It will be super fun! Follow me at www.twitch.tv/ohmytinytin to not miss the livestream :D or link in the bio <3

#lactoseintolerant #funnycomic #comic #comics #comix #cutecomics #relatablecomics

[Repost old comic till my arm heals] I will be streaming on twitch tonight at 8PM BST at www.twitch.tv/ohmytinytin! and I'll be doodling you guys and also my patrons :3 see you then!

Look at this lil burrito! Coco is happy burrito! :'D I love hugging and wrapping Coco in her clean fluffy blanket and making her cosy. Have any of you tried doing this with your pets? :3

If you have, do share some photos with me I'd love to see them burrito pets! ❤
